    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/c3f5bcd205d8df847bd3a222673ef5ba.avif?t=1756860539\" width=619 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款轻松的隐藏物品游戏，专为爱猫人士打造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在手绘场景中点击猫咪，找到它们全部吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/c08adad82f0a84d215a34dd8d880b8a9.avif?t=1756860539\" width=618 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😺 超过200只猫等你来找！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 4个场景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡  猫咪定位提示系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😻 发现特殊猫咪：当你返回已完成的关卡时，特殊猫咪将在场景中解锁。作为额外挑战，提示系统无法用于寻找这些特殊猫咪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/9a499095120a2d6c44cc83317a84bb24.poster.avif?t=1756860539\" width=620 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/9a499095120a2d6c44cc83317a84bb24.webm?t=1756860539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/9a499095120a2d6c44cc83317a84bb24.mp4?t=1756860539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔎 缩放功能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌗 对比度调节</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎵 轻松悦耳的音乐</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 除了小猫，每个关卡还隐藏着5个特殊物品等你发现（还有Steam成就奖励）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/e03fb2579d5848272c1a9211facc0c9c.poster.avif?t=1756860539\" width=664 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/e03fb2579d5848272c1a9211facc0c9c.webm?t=1756860539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/e03fb2579d5848272c1a9211facc0c9c.mp4?t=1756860539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 特别动画！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/96abb7f454140d103efad095f74860db.poster.avif?t=1756860539\" width=784 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/96abb7f454140d103efad095f74860db.webm?t=1756860539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/96abb7f454140d103efad095f74860db.mp4?t=1756860539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😸 喵喵声</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔉 音量控制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💾 存档与读取系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Steam成就</p></li></ul>",
